    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/arvylagunamayor/RobustErrorHandler</RepositoryUrl>
    <PackageDescription>Fork from https://github.com/AspNetCoreFromZeroToOverkill/GroupManagement, made some clean up to make the module reusable to different project without referencing the whole project </PackageDescription>
